%description
Provides a mechanism for easy computation of marketing metrics. By default
in this package, metrics for digital marketing (e.g. CTR (Click Through
Rate), CVR (Conversion Rate), CPC (Cost Per Click) etc) are calculated but
you can define your own metrics easily. In addition to that, you can
change an analysis axis to calculate these metrics.

